			[<a href="#">Change password</a>]<br/>
			<a href="#">Delete account</a> (confirmation required)<br/><br/>

			<h3>Forum activity</h3>
			Number of <a href="#">forum</a> posts:<br/>1<br/>
			Last forum post:<br/><a href="#">*NOOB* Why is there no category selection possible?</a><br/>
			</p>
		</div>
	
	</div>

